title: "Claude Code Failover Cockpit"
abstract: >-
  A resilient, anti-lock-in setup for running Claude Code as a single coding
  cockpit while falling back across model backends (Anthropic, AWS Bedrock,
  cheaper APIs via OpenRouter, and fully-local models) without changing the
  working environment.
type: software
